<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시판</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/board/css.css">
    <script src="js/board/write.js"defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="board_wrap">
        <div class="board_title">
            <strong>제품 등록</strong>
            <p>제품을 등록할수있는 공간입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="board_write_wrap">
            <div class="board_write">
                <div class="title">
                    <dl>
                        <dt>제품 이름</dt>
                        <dd><input class="tilte" type="text" placeholder="제품 이름"></dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
                <div class="info">
                    <dl>
                        <dt>글쓴이</dt>
                      <dd id="userid"><%=data[0].id %></dd>
                    </dl>
                    <dl>
                        <dt>희망가격</dt>
                        <dd><input  class="price" type="text" placeholder="가격 입력"> </dd>
                    </dl>
                    <input type="file" id="fileUpload" accept='image/jpeg,image/gif,image/png'>
                </div>
                <div class="cont">
                    <textarea class="content" placeholder="내용 입력"></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bt_wrap">
                <button  class="on">등록</button>
                <a>취소</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>